definition: Preferred form of name for use in Iowa State University Library metadata.

Duane H. Nash, Inc. is incorporated in 1905 upon death of Duane H. Nash (1843-1905). Nash Acme Harrow Company (Philadelphia, Pennsylvania) is incorporated in 1924 with Duane H. Nash, Jr., as sales manager.

alternative_form: Archived university websites; Archived university web sites
definition: Preferred genre term for use in Iowa State University Library metadata.
usage: Use this term to characterize resources created through web archiving. Apply this term to archived websites created by an institution of higher learning. This term should describe the overall type of website, not content or pages within a website. See related genre terms to ensure you select the most appropriate term for the resource.
source: Iowa State University. Special Collections and University Archives
